---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import company from '../data/company.json';
---
<BaseLayout title={`기술정보 | ${company.name}`} current="technology">
  <main>
    <section class="page-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="eyebrow">Technology</p>
        <h1>기술정보</h1>
        <p>나노소재, 인쇄전자, R&D 장비제조 영역에서 축적한 기술을 기반으로 연구 장비를 개발합니다.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="grid">
          {company.technologies.map((technology) => (
            <article class="detail-card">
              <h3>{technology}</h3>
            </article>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
